START
Enter / change ZQP sales order
Triggers USEREXIT_MOVE_FIELD_TO_VBAP
Fetch config from ZUPRGMVAR
Exit if no entries found or order type mismatch
Build plant range table
Exit if plant range is empty
Loop eligible order items
Plant in range, skip deleted items (UPDKZ = D)
Check SUB_NAME and SB partner
EMEA: SB partner required at item level
Read target item category
Look up HIGH value in LT_CONFIG using source PSTYV
Update item category
Set PSTYV to target. Set UPDKZ = U.
Clear variables and end loop
Clear all local variables and config tables
STOP
